                                                                                                                                Content display

                                                                                                                                Accordion 

                                                                                                                                Design beta

                                                                                                                                An accordion is a vertical stack of collapsible panels that allows users to expand or collapse each panel individually to reveal or hide their content. It typically presents content that is one level deep.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics

                                                                                                                                Cell size and spacing

                                                                                                                                The accordion comes in two different sizes: Standard and Compact. The main difference between the two sizes is the top and bottom padding.

                                                                                                                                Standard size accordion gives the cell more utility, while the Compact accordion allows more content display in limited vertical space.

                                                                                                                                Standard size accordion

                                                                                                                                • The standard list item has a minimum cell height of 64.

                                                                                                                                • Artwork size supports: small, medium, large, custom

                                                                                                                                • Leading text supports: Label, paragraph, supporting paragraph

                                                                                                                                • Trailing text supports: Label, paragraph

                                                                                                                                Compact size accordion

                                                                                                                                Compact list item has no minimum height and the cell height is always the tallest content with 12 top and bottom padding.

                                                                                                                                A compact size accordion can support small and medium artwork only. Large and custom artwork is supported by the standard size of the accordion.

                                                                                                                                Leading content

                                                                                                                                Artwork smaller than 36x36

                                                                                                                                For artwork sizes, up to 36 the artwork is centered in a 64 container. This behavior matches that of the Header component, so the navigation icon is always center aligned with list artwork.

                                                                                                                                Artwork larger than 36x36

                                                                                                                                For artwork larger than 36, the artwork has a 16 padding left and right. The padding can be adjusted if there is already proper spacing built into the artwork

                                                                                                                                Trailing content

                                                                                                                                Trailing content can be indicators or controls (24), badges of any kind, larger elements such as buttons or even more text content.

                                                                                                                                24x24 accordion icon

                                                                                                                                Icon is centered in a 64 container. This behavior matches that of the Header component so the action icon is always center-aligned with the accordion expand/collapse icon.

                                                                                                                                Inset Standard

                                                                                                                                Type and color

                                                                                                                                Keyboard accessibility

                                                                                                                                Web tabbing map


                                                                                                                                Collapsed accordion on focus

                                                                                                                                This is when the accordion is closed, and the user has tabbed to the panel using the tabbing map. If they were to click enter or space they would open the accordion panel.

                                                                                                                                Expanded accordion on focus

                                                                                                                                This is when the accordion is open, and the user has tabbed to the panel using the tabbing map. If they were to click enter or space on the heading area of the accordion, they would close the accordion panel.


                                                                                                                                If the user wants to navigate within the content of the panel, they can click tab

                                                                                                                                Collapsed view
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voice preview: "Gas prices $4.50/Regular. Button. Collapsed. Double-tap to expand."

                                                                                                                                Label: Gas prices $4.50 regular

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button

                                                                                                                                Value: Collapsed

                                                                                                                                Hint: Double-tap to expand.

                                                                                                                                Note: When the user double-taps to expand the accordion, focus should stay on the accordion's heading and VO should voice out that the panel has been expanded. "Gas prices $4.50 regular, Expanded."
